---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout 
  title="Web Design Service Areas Orange County CA | OCWebPros" 
  description="OCWebPros provides custom web design and local SEO services across Orange County, CA. Serving Lake Forest, Irvine, Mission Viejo, Rancho Santa Margarita, and all South OC cities. Local support, no overseas handoffs."
  bodyClass="page-service-areas">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages/services.css" />

  <header class="relative pt-32 sm:pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-12 sm:pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 text-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[90vw] max-w-[800px] h-[400px] sm:h-[500px] md:h-[600px] glow-bg pointer-events-none opacity-40"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        Service Areas
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Web Design Service Areas in <span class="text-gradient-orange">Orange County</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        OCWebPros is based in Lake Forest, CA and serves businesses across all of Orange County — with deep expertise in South OC markets.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="pb-16 sm:pb-24 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Intro paragraph -->
    <section class="pt-8 pb-12">
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Orange County is a diverse business landscape — from tech startups in Irvine to family‑owned restaurants in San Clemente, each market has unique needs. 
          As a Lake Forest‑based agency, we understand the local nuances that make OC businesses successful.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We provide <strong>custom web design</strong> and <strong>local SEO services</strong> to businesses across the county, with a focus on cities where we've built the deepest expertise.
          Every website we build is optimized for local search, mobile‑first, and designed to convert visitors into customers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Primary Service Areas -->
    <section class="pt-8 pb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Primary Service Areas</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-12 text-lg">
        These are the cities where we've completed the most projects and developed deep local market knowledge.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Lake Forest -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Our Home Base
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Lake Forest</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            OCWebPros is based right here in Lake Forest. We know the local business community — from the Foothill Ranch Tech Park to the Saddleback Valley Plaza.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            Lake Forest businesses benefit from our hyper‑local understanding of South OC consumer behavior and search trends.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request Lake Forest Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Irvine -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Tech & Startup Hub
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Irvine</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Irvine's competitive business environment demands websites that stand out. We build custom sites for Irvine companies that need to compete with national brands.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            From the Irvine Spectrum to the John Wayne Airport area, we understand the premium expectations of Irvine consumers and businesses.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request Irvine Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission Viejo -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Family‑Focused Community
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Mission Viejo</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Mission Viejo's family‑oriented market values trust and local connection. Our websites for Mission Viejo businesses emphasize community relevance and ease of use.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            Whether you're near the Mission Viejo Mall or the Lake, we build sites that resonate with South OC families.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request Mission Viejo Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Rancho Santa Margarita -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Growing South OC City
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Rancho Santa Margarita</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            RSM's tight‑knit business community values personalized service. As neighbors in Lake Forest, we provide the local touch RSM businesses expect.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            From the Trabuco Canyon area to the Central Park, we understand RSM's unique market dynamics.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request RSM Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Laguna Hills -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Medical & Professional Hub
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Laguna Hills</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Laguna Hills' concentration of medical practices and professional services requires websites that build credibility and facilitate patient/client communication.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            Near the Laguna Hills Mall and Saddleback Memorial, we build sites that meet the high standards of Laguna Hills professionals.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request Laguna Hills Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Aliso Viejo -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 border border-orange-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-orange-400 mb-4">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-orange-500"></span>
            Modern Suburban Center
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Aliso Viejo</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Aliso Viejo's newer developments and corporate centers demand modern, responsive web design. We build sites that match Aliso Viejo's contemporary aesthetic.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
            From the Town Center to the Aliso Creek Business District, we understand the expectations of Aliso Viejo businesses and residents.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 font-medium hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors">
            Request Aliso Viejo Consultation →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Additional Cities Served -->
    <section class="pt-8 pb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Also Serving These Orange County Cities</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 text-lg">
        While our deepest expertise is in South OC, we provide web design and SEO services to businesses throughout Orange County.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">San Clemente</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Dana Point</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">San Juan Capistrano</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Laguna Beach</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Laguna Niguel</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Newport Beach</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Costa Mesa</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Tustin</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Orange</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <div class="text-white font-medium">Fullerton</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="pt-12 pb-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-600/20 to-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Grow Your Orange County Business?</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Whether you're in Lake Forest, Irvine, Mission Viejo, or anywhere in Orange County — we build websites that rank, convert, and grow with your business.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="px-8 py-4 bg-orange-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl btn-glow hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors text-center">
            Get a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-center">
            View Our Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>